title: Salinas Pueblo Missions National Monument: News
body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     News             News       The National Park Service makes every effort to keep the public informed about news events and special and re-occurring events which occur within and around the units of the Park Service.  Â        Subscribe  | What is RSS     April 25, 2016  Tourism to Salinas Pueblo Missions National Monument creates $2,182,700 in Economic Benefits Report shows visitor spending supports 28 jobs in local economy  "Salinas Pueblo Missions National Monument welcomes visitors from across the country and around the world," said Acting Superintendent Patrick Malone.
